            <div class="container">
                
                <p class="title_purple_30px text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</p>
                <div class="accordion accordion-flush" id="accordion">
                <div class="accordion-item">
<h4 class="accordion-header" id="heading0"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse0" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse0"><span>Provide details about Podar International School?</span></button></h4>
<div class="accordion-collapse collapse" id="collapse0" aria-labelledby="heading0" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
<div class="accordion-body">
<p>Welcome to Podar International School! As parents and guardians, you want to give your children the best of everything- quality education, a safe and nurturing environment and means to live a well-balanced, holistic life. By enrolling your children at Podar International School, you will be taking the first step towards a bright future for your children.</p>
<p>With 99 years of expertise in the field of learning, Podar International School is considered among the best CBSE, ICSE and International schools in India. The Podar group has under its wings:</p>
<ul>
     <li>A combined student strength of more than 2,75,000</li>
     <li>Support of 8,000 dedicated and loyal staff members.</li>
</ul>
<p>Offering learning programs from pre-primary to class 12, we&#8217;re among the best and all-encompassing schools in India. Considered among the pioneers of education in India, Podar offers a plethora of educational streams such as:</p>
<ul>
     <li>Central Board of Secondary Education (CBSE)</li>
     <li>Council for the Indian School Certificate Examinations (CISCE)</li>
     <li>Secondary School Certificate (SSC)</li>
     <li>Cambridge (IGCSE)</li>
     <li>International Baccalaureate (IB)</li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-item">
<h4 class="accordion-header" id="heading1"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse1" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse1"><span>Why Choose Podar International School?</span></button></h4>
<div class="accordion-collapse collapse" id="collapse1" aria-labelledby="heading1" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
<div class="accordion-body">
<p>We believe in holistic learning. While we want your child to excel in academics, we also don&#8217;t want them to diminish their passion. Our job, as an educational institute, is to prepare the young minds of today for a bright tomorrow. Hence, we focus on creating all-rounders.</p>
<p>Thanks to the variety of boards offered, as parents you have the choice to select between multiple options, all under one umbrella. Podar is considered among the best CBSE schools in India, and the best ICSE schools in India in addition to holding its position among the top international schools in India. Why so? Because of the quality of education we provide. Our innovative learning methods, equal focus on academics and extracurricular, and a strong curriculum all together are a perfect combination for growth and success.</p>
<p>Through the Podar Innovation center, 80+ academicians have come together to create a curriculum and content based on the guidelines of various boards including CBSE, ICSE, CAIE and the Maharashtra State Board. Apart from offering a strong syllabus and curriculum, the PIC also offers facilities and programs such as remedial learning that help teachers in assisting students to cope with difficult concepts, symphonic, math gym, math lab and life skills that are appropriate for their future and help them in becoming independent.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-item">
<h4 class="accordion-header" id="heading2"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse2" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse2"><span>What Sets Podar International School Apart?</span></button></h4>
<div class="accordion-collapse collapse" id="collapse2" aria-labelledby="heading2" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
<div class="accordion-body">
<p>When we call ourselves pioneers and cheerleaders of education in India, we take those monikers seriously. We want to make learning accessible to all, and for that we will have to spread our wings. Podar International School is present across the length and breadth of the country through multiple branches. This makes education accessible to everyone.</p>
<p>Besides, we also understand that in today&#8217;s day and age, most parents are also chasing their own careers while trying to give their kids the best quality of life and education. To aid them in their journey and not stop them from realizing their dreams, the presence of Podar International School in various parts of the country gives it an edge. If you&#8217;re a parent in a transferable job, enrolling your child in our school will help you pick up the next best opportunity as we have branches across multiple cities and states. Once your child is a part of the Podar Education Network, it will be easier for you to re-enroll them in a hassle-free manner in one of the top schools in India.</p>
<p>The icing on the cake, needless to say, is the Podar Innovation Centre that helps bind us all. A centralized learning centre makes the job easier for the teachers, students, and parents. Add to it our strong parent-teacher community that comes together often to ensure they&#8217;re on the same page and to discuss all the different ways they can make school life easy and fun for children.</p>
<p>In summation, at Podar:</p>
<ul>
     <li>We&#8217;re technology first</li>
     <li>Have state-of-the-art infrastructure</li>
     <li>Have provisions for Indoor and outdoor games</li>
     <li>Have a stress-free and clean environment</li>
     <li>Well-equipped, ventilated, and spacious classrooms</li>
</ul>
<p>And so much more.</p>
<p>For those interested in admitting their kids to our school, our admission process is swift and easy. Please visit https://www.podareducation.org/admissions for more information.</p>
<!--
<p>Podar International is considered among the top Indian schools of today's times, and has a wide presence around the country. We have schools in some of the top Indian cities such as:</p>
<ul>
     <li><a href="/schools-in-mumbai">Schools in Mumbai</a></li>
     <li><a href="/schools-in-mumbai">Schools in Pune</a></li>
     <li><a href="/schools-in-mumbai">Schools in Nagpur</a></li>
     <li><a href="/schools-in-mumbai">Schools in Chhatrapati Sambhaji Nagar</a></li>
     <li><a href="/schools-in-mumbai">Schools in Nashik</a></li>
     <li><a href="/schools-in-mumbai">Schools in Thane</a></li>
     <li><a href="/schools-in-mumbai">Schools in Navi Mumbai</a></li>
     <li><a href="/schools-in-mumbai">Schools in Ahmedabad</a></li>
     <li><a href="/schools-in-mumbai">Schools in Bengaluru</a></li>
</ul>
-->
<p>Apart from these, we're present in multiple other locations across the country.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-item">
<h4 class="accordion-header" id="heading3"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse3" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse3"><span>Is Podar International School private?</span></button></h4>
<div class="accordion-collapse collapse" id="collapse3" aria-labelledby="heading3" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
<div class="accordion-body">
<p>Yes. All Podar International Schools in India are privately owned and managed.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-item">
<h4 class="accordion-header" id="heading4"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse4" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse4"><span>Which board does Podar school have?</span></button></h4>
<div class="accordion-collapse collapse" id="collapse4" aria-labelledby="heading4" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
<div class="accordion-body">
<p>The Podar Network of Schools provides a diverse range of educational opportunities, including the Central Board of Secondary Education (CBSE), the Council for the Indian School Certificate Examinations (CISCE), the Secondary School Certificate (SSC), Cambridge (IGCSE), and the International Baccalaureate (IB).</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-item">
<h4 class="accordion-header" id="heading5"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse5" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse5"><span>How many branches are there of Podar International School in India?</span></button></h4>
<div class="accordion-collapse collapse" id="collapse5" aria-labelledby="heading5" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
<div class="accordion-body">
<p>There are 165 Podar International Schools located all over the country.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-item">
<h4 class="accordion-header" id="heading6"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse6" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse6"><span>Who is the owner / Trustee of Podar International School?</span></button></h4>
<div class="accordion-collapse collapse" id="collapse6" aria-labelledby="heading6" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
<div class="accordion-body">
<p>Dr. Pavan Podar is the Chairman of Podar Education Network.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="accordion-item">
<h4 class="accordion-header" id="heading7"><button class="accordion-button collapsed" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#collapse7" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="collapse7"><span>How can I get admission in Podar school?</span></button></h4>
<div class="accordion-collapse collapse" id="collapse7" aria-labelledby="heading7" data-bs-parent="#accordion">
<div class="accordion-body">
<p>The admission process is simple. Admissions are on a first come first serve basis in Podar International School. Requesting you to please contact the school office for more information - <a href="https://www.podareducation.org/locations" target="_blank">https://www.podareducation.org/locations</a>. Admissions are also available online. Please visit <a href="https://www.podareducation.org/admissions" target="_blank">https://www.podareducation.org/admissions</a> for more information.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>

                    
                </div>
            </div>
</section>

